HEADWORD: free-enterprise
<hw>free-enterprise</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to the
<er>free enterprise</er> system having private ownership of the means of
production and competition between enterprises.</def>
<mark>[prenominal]</mark> [Narrower terms: <stype>capitalistic,
capitalist</stype>] <ant>socialistic</ant>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> competitive,
private-enterprise(prenominal).</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

